It gets annoying hitting 'Yes' to the delete confirmation when testing the dynamic tasklist. It would be better if you could turn this off with a macro parameter.

{dynamictasklist:My tasklist|promptOnDelete=false}

Because the name of the tasklist is always the first parameter, your tasklist must have a name to use this parameter.

